apt-clone (0.2) UNRELEASED; urgency=lowbv

  * apt_clone.py:
    - maverick tarfile seems to cut off the "./" of the path, auto
      detect that
    - when runing in normal restore mode, use disable auto_inst and 
      auto_fix until everything is installed, this assume the clone
      is consistent
  * apt_clone.py, tests/test_clone.py: 
    - add _find_modified_conffiles helper and test for that

